{"type":"message","id":"c1bf1779","parentId":"508c80c7","timestamp":"2026-03-16T00:01:55.872Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Daily report for March 15, 2026 has been sent to Allan via Feishu.\n\n**Summary:**\n- Gathered data from `memory/daily/2026-03-15.md`, `diary/2026-03-15.md`, and morning chat logs\n- Checked OpenClaw PR #24218 — **CLOSED** (fix for sub-agent workspace config by Zephyr Cao, merged Feb 27)\n- Key highlights: LCM preserve tag implementation (PR #78), Whitepaper Chapter 5 complete, did:clawish spec drafted\n- Report delivered to Allan via Feishu direct message"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":55351,"output":134,"cacheRead":7488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62973,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773619301867}}
